Building InfiniteRicks

See doc/readme-qt.rst for instructions on building InfiniteRicks QT,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of InfiniteRicks.

See doc/build-*.txt for instructions on building InfiniteRicksd,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of InfiniteRicks.
